{
    "chapter": 55,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "55:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>至仁主有着宽广的仁慈，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "55:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂以容易背记和理解的《古兰经》传授了人类。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "55:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂创造了人类，并完美其形态，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "55:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂教授人类怎样以语言和书写阐明心中所想，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "55:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂使太阳和月亮按照精细的定数运行，以便人们计年和计数。</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "55:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>没有腿脚的植物和树木，顺从地向清高的真主叩头。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "55:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂升起天空作为大地的顶，并在大地上以公正命令众仆遵守。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "55:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！祂规定公正，以便你们不要在称量计数时欺诈。</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "55:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们当给予彼此公正的分量，在为他人称量时，不要缺斤短两。</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "55:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂把大地造成适宜万生安居的环境，</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "55:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>地上有结出果实的树木，有枝条上长结椰枣的椰枣树，</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "55:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有像小麦和大麦一样你们享受其种子的，还有享受其香味的各类植物。</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "55:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "55:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>祂从能听见响声的干土中创造了阿丹（愿主赐其平安）。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "55:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>从纯烟的焰火中创造了精灵之父。</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "55:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "55:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他是养育冬季和夏季东升和西落太阳的主。</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "55:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "55:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主使咸水和淡水的海洋在肉眼看不到的地方相会。</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "55:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>两海之间有一道阻止二者相互流通的屏障，以便两海之水互不侵染。</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "55:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "55:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>大小珍珠出自两海汇合处。</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "55:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "55:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>惟清高的真主掌握着海洋里航行的如同山峰一样高大的船舶。</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "55:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "55:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！大地上所有被造物必将毁灭，</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "55:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！惟有对众仆博施恩惠的主尊严永存，永不消失。</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "55:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "55:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>诸天中的所有天使、大地上的所有精灵和人类都向祂祈求自己所需，祂每天都在经营众仆的事务，其中有生存、死亡和给养等。</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "55:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "55:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！我将专门清算你们，以你们所应得的进行赏罚。</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "55:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "55:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活日，精灵和人类被集合时，真主将说：“精灵和人类啊！假若你们能在诸天和大地上发现任何一处躲避所，你们就躲避吧！唯权力和明证能使你们做到，然而，你们怎会有那些权力和明证呢？</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "55:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "55:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！真主将派遣无烟的纯火和无焰的烟来临你们，对此，你们无法阻挡。</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "55:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "55:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当天空因众天使从中降下而破裂之时，它是红色的，其颜色如红色染料一般。</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "55:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "55:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在那重大的日子里，任何人和精灵的罪过都不被询问，因为真主自知一切。</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "55:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "55:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活日，犯罪者以他们的标志而辨识，即黑色的面孔和绿色的眼睛，他们的额头和脚被绑在一起，然后被扔进火狱。</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "55:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人类和精灵啊！你们到底是否认真主给予你们诸多恩惠中的哪项呢？</p>"
